<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Talk:Second_Amendment_to_the_United_States_Constitution"><a href="#Smears_aimed_at_Michael_Bellesiles" title="Talk:Second Amendment to the United States Constitution">Talk:Second Amendment to the United States Constitution</a></span></h2>

