<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Roger_Chiang">Roger Chiang</span></h2>

<p> </p>
<p>While cleaning out the catchall <a href="" title="Category:American criminals">Category:American criminals</a> I came across Roger Chiang. The article was peppered with dozens of recently added {fact} tags along with older hat tags.<a class="externallink" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;oldid=281075387" rel="nofollow" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;oldid=281075387"><a class="externallink" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;oldid=281075387" rel="nofollow" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;oldid=281075387">http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;oldid=281075387</a></a> After investigating briefly I decided first to revert to an earlier version and then to delete large unsourced or POV portions, including some that made negative assertions about 3rd parties.<a class="externallink" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;diff=281454936&#38;oldid=281075387" rel="nofollow" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;diff=281454936&#38;oldid=281075387"><a class="externallink" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;diff=281454936&#38;oldid=281075387" rel="nofollow" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;diff=281454936&#38;oldid=281075387">http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;diff=281454936&#38;oldid=281075387</a></a><a class="externallink" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;diff=281456115&#38;oldid=281454936" rel="nofollow" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;diff=281456115&#38;oldid=281454936"><a class="externallink" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;diff=281456115&#38;oldid=281454936" rel="nofollow" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Roger_Chiang&#38;diff=281456115&#38;oldid=281454936">http://en.wiki