<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Semiprotect_Phil_Spector.E2.80.8E.3F">Semiprotect Phil Spector‎?</span></h2>

<p> 
Could we have a few days of semiprotection on  ?  In the wake of today&#39;s guilty verdict, it is hard to stem the tide of IP-editor vandalism. <a href="" title="User:TJRC">TJRC</a> (<a href="" title="User talk:TJRC">talk</a>) 21:43, 13 April 2009 (UTC)</p>

<dl>
