<dd>Well, the reason given isn&#39;t valid. Wikipedia is written from sources, not subjects. The article, in my opinion, doesn&#39;t qualify for CSD. Best to open an AFD and let it be known that the subject requests deletion. <a href="" title="User:Jennavecia">&#60;span style=&#34;font-family:Lucida Handwriting Italic;color:#9B30FF&#34;&#62;<b>ل</b>enna&#60;/span&#62;</a><a href="" title="User talk:Jennavecia">&#60;span style=&#34;font-family:Lucida Handwriting Italic;color:#63B8FF&#34;&#62;vecia&#60;/span&#62;</a> 15:20, 13 April 2009 (UTC)</dd></dl>


