<dd>
<dl>
<dd>
<dl>
<dd>Oh, btw, the chap is not edit warring to keep clear BLP violations on the page. Can people watch list the article? We don&#39;t want our articles to take the POV of the SPLC as factual.--<a href="" title="User talk:Scott MacDonald">Scott Mac (Doc)</a> 01:57, 10 April 2009 (UTC)</dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl>

